      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>See My IP v0.2</h2>
        <p>Automatic updates, a new app icon, and stability fixes.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Sparkle-based automatic update support with signed releases</li>
          <li>Updated app icon across the macOS app bundle</li>
          <li>More consistent network refresh state after connectivity changes</li>
          <li>Corrected short history durations and compressed IPv6 masking</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
